TEXT.TITLE: NO AUSTRALIAN TREASURY NOTE TENDER NEXT WEEK
TEXT.BODY: The Reserve Bank said it will not offer any treasury notes for tender next week. Last week the Bank offered 400 mln dlrs of 13-week notes and 100 mln dlrs of 26-week notes. Analysts said the Bank's decision not to offer stock next week reflects the higher demand for funds at the start of the system of provisional tax payments. REUTER
